[I] Secure Boot key manager

[T] sbctl intends to be a user-friendly secure boot key manager capable of
[T] setting up secure boot, offer key management capabilities, and keep track
[T] of files that needs to be signed in the boot chain.

[U] https://github.com/Foxboron/sbctl

[A] Foxboron
[M] The T2 Project <t2@t2-project.org>

[C] extra/security
[F] CROSS

[L] MIT
[S] Beta
